msgid "<em>Note.</em>"
msgstr "<em>Catatan.</em>"

msgid "no plot object was found"
msgstr "objek diagram tidak ditemukan"

msgid "The following problem(s) occurred while running the analysis:"
msgstr "Masalah berikut ini terjadi saat menjalankan analisis:"

msgid "after grouping on %s"
msgstr "setelah pengelompokan pada %s"

msgid ""
"This analysis terminated unexpectedly. %s To receive assistance with this "
"problem, please report the message above at: https://jasp-stats.org/bug-"
"reports"
msgstr ""
"Analisis ini dihentikan secara tidak terduga. %s Untuk mendapatkan bantuan "
"atas masalah ini, silakan laporkan pesan di atas di: https://jasp-stats.org/"
"bug-reports"

msgid "Infinity found in %s"
msgstr "Tak terhingga ditemukan di %s"

msgid "Number of factor levels is %1$s in %2$s"
msgstr "Jumlah tingkat faktor adalah %1$s di %2$s"

msgid "The variance in %1$s is equal to %2$s"
msgstr "Varians di %1$s sama dengan %2$s"

msgid "Number of observations is %1$s in %2$s"
msgstr "Jumlah observasi adalah %1$s di %2$s"

msgid ""
"Cannot compute statistic reliably: number of observations is %1$s in %2$s"
msgstr ""
"Statistik tidak dapat dihitung secara andal: jumlah observasi adalah %1$s di "
"%2$s"

msgid "Values in %1$s outside interval [%2$s, %3$s]"
msgstr "Nilai di %1$s di luar interval [%2$s, %3$s]"

msgid ""
"Dataset is not a proper variance-covariance matrix. Please load only a "
"positive definite symmetrical matrix as your dataset."
msgstr ""
"Dataset ini bukan matriks varians-kovarians yang tepat. Silakan hanya memuat "
"matriks simetris definit positif sebagai dataset Anda."

msgid ""
"The variance-covariance matrix of the supplied data is not positive-"
"definite. Please check if variables have many missings observations or are "
"collinear"
msgstr ""
"Matriks varians-kovarians dari data yang diberikan bukan matriks definit "
"positif. Silakan periksa apakah variabel memiliki banyak observasi yang "
"hilang atau kolinear"

msgid ""
"Main effects and lower-order interactions must be included whenever the "
"corresponding higher-order interaction is included"
msgstr ""
"Efek utama dan interaksi tingkat rendah harus disertakan setiap kali "
"interaksi tingkat tinggi yang terkait disertakan"

msgid "Negative numbers found in %s"
msgstr "Bilangan negatif ditemukan dalam %s"

msgid "Missing values encountered in %s"
msgstr "Nilai yang hilang ditemukan di %s"

msgid "Duplicate variables encountered in %s"
msgstr "Variabel ganda terjadi di %s"

msgid ""
"Over %s%% of the rows consist entirely of missing values. Please remove "
"these rows from the data set if you wish to continue."
msgstr ""
"Lebih dari %s%% baris seluruhnya berisi nilai yang hilang. Silakan hapus "
"baris ini dari kumpulan data jika Anda ingin melanjutkan."

msgid ""
"Levene's test is significant (p < .05), suggesting a violation of the equal "
"variance assumption"
msgstr ""
"Uji Levene signifikan (p < .05), menyarankan pelanggaran asumsi kesamaan "
"varians"

msgid ""
"Vovk-Sellke Maximum <em>p</em>-Ratio: Based on the <em>p</em>-value, the "
"maximum possible odds in favor of H%1$s over H%2$s equals 1/(-e <em>p</em> "
"log(<em>p</em>)) for <em>p</em> %3$s .37 (Sellke, Bayarri, & Berger, 2001)."
msgstr ""
"Rasio <em>p</em> Maksimum Vovk-Sellke: Berdasarkan nilai <em>p</em>, peluang "
"maksimum yang mungkin menguntungkan H%1$s dibandingkan H%2$s sama dengan 1/(-"
"e <em>p</em> log(<em>p</em>)) untuk <em>p</em> %3$s 0,37 (Sellke, Bayarri, & "
"Berger, 2001)."

msgid "Proportions tested against value: %s"
msgstr "Proporsi yang diuji terhadap nilai: %s"

msgid ""
"For all tests, the alternative hypothesis specifies that the proportion is "
"less than %s"
msgstr ""
"Untuk semua pengujian, hipotesis alternatif menetapkan bahwa proporsinya "
"kurang dari %s"

msgid ""
"For all tests, the alternative hypothesis specifies that the proportion is "
"greater than %s"
msgstr ""
"Untuk semua pengujian, hipotesis alternatif menetapkan bahwa proporsinya "
"lebih besar dari %s"

msgid "Could not find message for class %1$s and type %2$s"
msgstr "Pesan untuk kelas %1$s dan jenis %2$s tidak ditemukan"

msgid "The following error occured while converting a ggplot to plotly: %s"
msgstr "Terjadi galat berikut saat mengonversikan ggplot ke plotly: %s"

msgid "No interactive plot generated..."
msgstr ""

